---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import CallToAction from '../components/CallToAction.astro';

const title = "SEO Strategy & Technical Optimization - Alpha Performance Lab";
const description = "Comprehensive SEO strategy for dominating search rankings and driving organic traffic to our Edison Wave affiliate site.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        SEO Strategy & Technical Optimization
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10">
        Phase C: Steps 141-150 - Dominating search rankings for Edison Wave affiliate keywords.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <h2>Primary Keyword Strategy (Step 141)</h2>
        <p>
          Our SEO strategy focuses on capturing high-intent keywords related to The Edison Wave and brainwave entrainment.
        </p>
        
        <h3>Primary Target Keywords:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>"Edison Wave Review"</strong> - High commercial intent, moderate competition</li>
          <li><strong>"Edison Wave Scam"</strong> - Capturing negative sentiment searches</li>
          <li><strong>"Edison Wave vs Brain.fm"</strong> - Comparison searches</li>
          <li><strong>"Alpha Wave Entrainment"</strong> - Educational/informational</li>
          <li><strong>"Best Brainwave App"</strong> - Broad commercial intent</li>
          <li><strong>"Binaural Beats for Focus"</strong> - Specific use case</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Long-tail Keywords:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>"Edison Wave honest review 2024"</li>
          <li>"Does Edison Wave really work for focus"</li>
          <li>"Edison Wave vs other brainwave apps"</li>
          <li>"Alpha wave training for productivity"</li>
          <li>"Best binaural beats for studying"</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Technical SEO Implementation (Steps 142-145)</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 142: Site Structure & URL Optimization</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">URL Structure:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li><code>/review</code> - Main pillar page</li>
              <li><code>/science-of-alpha-waves</code> - Supporting content</li>
              <li><code>/blog/[topic]</code> - Supporting articles</li>
              <li><code>/frequency-explorer</code> - Interactive tool</li>
              <li><code>/bonuses</code> - Conversion-focused page</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 143: Meta Tags & Schema Markup</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Implementation:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Unique title tags for each page (50-60 characters)</li>
              <li>Compelling meta descriptions (150-160 characters)</li>
              <li>Schema markup for reviews, articles, and organization</li>
              <li>Open Graph tags for social sharing</li>
              <li>Twitter Card optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 144: Site Speed & Core Web Vitals</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Optimization Targets:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li><strong>LCP (Largest Contentful Paint):</strong> &lt; 2.5 seconds</li>
              <li><strong>FID (First Input Delay):</strong> &lt; 100ms</li>
              <li><strong>CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift):</strong> &lt; 0.1</li>
              <li>Image optimization and lazy loading</li>
              <li>Minimal JavaScript bundles</li>
              <li>CDN optimization via Cloudflare</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 145: Mobile Optimization</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mobile-First Approach:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Responsive design with Tailwind CSS</li>
              <li>Touch-friendly navigation and buttons</li>
              <li>Optimized font sizes and spacing</li>
              <li>Fast mobile loading times</li>
              <li>Mobile-specific UX improvements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Content SEO Strategy (Steps 146-148)</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 146: Keyword Integration</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Content Optimization:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Primary keyword in H1 tag</li>
              <li>Secondary keywords in H2/H3 tags</li>
              <li>Natural keyword density (1-2%)</li>
              <li>LSI keywords for semantic relevance</li>
              <li>Keyword variations throughout content</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 147: Internal Linking Strategy</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Link Architecture:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Hub-and-spoke model with /review as hub</li>
              <li>Contextual internal links</li>
              <li>Anchor text optimization</li>
              <li>Related content suggestions</li>
              <li>Breadcrumb navigation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 148: Content Freshness & Updates</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Maintenance Strategy:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Regular content updates and refreshes</li>
              <li>New blog posts weekly</li>
              <li>Updated review sections</li>
              <li>Current year references</li>
              <li>Seasonal content adjustments</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Link Building Strategy (Steps 149-150)</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 149: Outreach & Guest Content</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Link Building Tactics:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Guest posts on productivity and wellness blogs</li>
              <li>Podcast appearances discussing brainwave science</li>
              <li>Resource page link requests</li>
              <li>Broken link building</li>
              <li>Digital PR and expert quotes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Step 150: Local SEO & Citations</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local Optimization:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Google My Business optimization</li>
              <li>Local directory submissions</li>
              <li>Citation building</li>
              <li>Local keyword targeting</li>
              <li>Reviews and reputation management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>SEO Tools & Monitoring</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Essential Tools</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li><strong>Google Search Console:</strong> Performance monitoring</li>
              <li><strong>Google Analytics 4:</strong> Traffic analysis</li>
              <li><strong>Ahrefs/SEMrush:</strong> Keyword research</li>
              <li><strong>PageSpeed Insights:</strong> Performance testing</li>
              <li><strong>Schema Markup Validator:</strong> Structured data</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">KPIs to Track</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li><strong>Organic Traffic:</strong> Monthly growth</li>
              <li><strong>Keyword Rankings:</strong> Target keyword positions</li>
              <li><strong>Click-Through Rate:</strong> SERP performance</li>
              <li><strong>Conversion Rate:</strong> Organic to affiliate</li>
              <li><strong>Domain Authority:</strong> Overall site strength</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Competitive Analysis & Positioning</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Competitor SEO Analysis</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Key Competitors:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li><strong>Brain.fm:</strong> Direct product competitor</li>
              <li><strong>Focus@Will:</strong> Similar brainwave app</li>
              <li><strong>Noisli:</strong> Ambient sound competitor</li>
              <li><strong>Other Edison Wave affiliates:</strong> Direct competition</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">
              Analyze their keyword strategies, content gaps, and link profiles to identify opportunities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Implementation Timeline</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Phase C SEO Roadmap</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Weeks 1-2 (Steps 141-145):</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Technical SEO implementation</li>
              <li>Site speed optimization</li>
              <li>Mobile optimization</li>
              <li>Schema markup implementation</li>
            </ul>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 mt-4">Weeks 3-4 (Steps 146-150):</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Content optimization</li>
              <li>Internal linking strategy</li>
              <li>Link building outreach</li>
              <li>Local SEO setup</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CallToAction />
</MainLayout>
